description:
Discover Amir's Amazing Argan Oil Shampoo and Conditioner. 
Argan Oil is produced from the kernels of the Argania Spinosa tree found in Morocco. Argan Oil has become known world wide to be nature's finest

Acai Berry is produced from the berries of the Acai Palm found in the Amazon Rain Forest. Acai berry possesses a combination of essential fatty acids,
